"""
# FFI Generator System Test

**Feature IDs:** #905-906
**Category:** Tooling
**Difficulty:** 2/5
**Status:** Ready for compiled mode

## Overview

End-to-end system tests for the FFI generator pipeline.
These tests require compiled mode as the ffi_gen modules
are not available in interpreter mode.
"""

use std.spec

describe "FFI Generator Pipeline":
    it "requires compiled mode":
        # All FFI generator tests need compiled mode to access app.ffi_gen modules
        val mode_requirement = "compiled mode required for app.ffi_gen modules"
        expect(mode_requirement).to_contain("compiled mode")
